author: HBO Max
description:
In Episode 7 of the Peacemaker Podcast, James Gunn, co-hosts Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt), and Steve Agee (John Economos), with special guest Danielle Brooks (Leota Adebayo) unpack Season 1, Episode 7, "Stop Dragon My Heart Around" The discussion opens with Danielle’s journey joining the cast, including her nerves about entering the comic book world and her excitement at playing Viola Davis’ daughter. They explore Peacemaker’s traumatic childhood, the tragic loss of his brother, and the complex relationships between parents and children. They cover the team’s confrontation over betrayal, the iconic slow-walk scene, and the heartfelt moment when Peacemaker’s side-kick, Eagly, makes his miraculous recovery. Conversation about faith, miracles, and friendship help round out episode 7 of the Peacemaker Podcast. Subscribe for more easter eggs and behind-the-scenes breakdowns. New episodes drop Mondays and Thursdays. Stream Peacemaker on HBO Max.
